gw.api.policy.refresh.pcintegration

Class PCPolicyGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.policy.refresh.pcintegration.PCPolicyGraph

  • public class PCPolicyGraph
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsible for building the bounding graph using the XSD types from the pcintegration web service and the NameTranslator to get the corresponding entity types.
